     P trimConv        B
     D trimConv        PI             1N
     D  pTgt                           *   Value
     D  trimSz                       10i 0
     D  nMax                         10i 0 Value
     D  pad                          10i 0 Value
     D  cntCCSID                     10i 0 Value
